headline: TransDigm (TDG): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: TransDigm currently trades at $1,377 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a middling return of 2.8%. However, the stock is beating the S&P 500’s 5.4% decline during that period.
